## 📚 API Documentation

### Endpoints

- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /tasks` - List available tasks
- `POST /reset` - Initialize environment
- `POST /step` - Execute action
- `GET /state` - Get environment state

### Response Format

```json
{
  "observation": {
    "tickets": [...],
    "task_id": "sentiment_recovery",
    "step_number": 1,
    "max_steps": 8,
    "available_actions": ["respond", "escalate", "compensate", "resolve", "defer"],
    "current_score": 0.625
  },
  "reward": {
    "score": 0.625,
    "partial_scores": {"sentiment_change": 0.25},
    "feedback": "Sentiment changed by 0.25.",
    "cumulative_score": 0.625
  },
  "done": false,
  "info": {}
}
```

