## 🧪 Testing

```bash
# Run verification tests
python customer-support-env/verify_scores.py

# Run improved inference baseline
python customer-support-env/inference.py

# Test with LLM agent
python customer-support-env/llm_agent.py
```

## 🔧 Configuration

Environment variables:
```bash
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:7860
MODEL_NAME=gpt-3.5-turbo
HF_TOKEN=your-api-key
DB_PATH=./data/sessions.db
```

## 📖 Project Structure

```
SupportSentinelEnv/
├── server/
│   └── app.py                 # FastAPI application
├── customer-support-env/
│   ├── environment.py         # Base environment
│   ├── graders.py             # Task scoring logic
│   ├── llm_agent.py           # LLM agent implementation
│   ├── tasks.py               # Task definitions
│   ├── models.py              # Data models
│   └── persistence.py         # Database layer
├── Dockerfile                 # Container configuration
├── docker-compose.yml         # Multi-container setup
├── start_server.ps1           # Windows startup script
├── requirements.txt           # Python dependencies
└── README.md                  # This file
```

